metadata.synopsis: The warning guard at the vault redirects the player to the main guard
metadata.how_to_trigger: - Load up GustavDev/CTY_Main_A- Run up to  |Vault Cashguard| - S_LOW_CountingHouse_VaultMainGuard - 936953b6-059b-4ed6-b03a-5d1b340f8889 - (-128 1 -234) while another guard at the gate is busy

0.speaker: Cashguard Artillerist Dadger
0.text: Steer clear of the other crowd below, if I may. Don't think I'd trust them around an open vault.

1.speaker: Cashguard Artillerist Dadger
1.text: Talk to the other one. He's the ranking officer, apparently.

2.speaker: Cashguard Artillerist Dadger
2.text: Talk to the other one. I'm just paid to stand glower. And not very well, at that.
